## Skills Practiced

- VLSM deployment
- Router configuration
- Switch management
- NAT Overload (PAT)
- DHCP configuration
- ACL modification
- Routing verification
- Connectivity testing
- Layer 2 verification

---

## Outcome

Successfully migrated the Castle Rysen District Shop network from the previous addressing scheme to the new **10.0.18.0/26** subnet.

The network now provides:

- Logical infrastructure addressing
- DHCP client addressing
- NAT Internet access
- Proper routing
- Successful Layer 2 and Layer 3 connectivity